HEADWORD: Shelterless
<hw>Shel"ter*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Destitute of shelter or
protection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Now sad and <qex>shelterless</qex> perhaps she lies.</q>
<rj><qau>Rowe.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

